<html>
    <Title>HTML Food Recipe</Title>
    <head> <h1> Recipe : MASALA MILK TEA </h1></head>
    <body>
        <h2>Masala Milk Tea ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li> Water </li>
            <li>Whole Milk</li>
            <li>Lipton Black Tea</li>
            <li>Brown Sugar</li>
            <li>Cinnamon and Cardamon</li>

        </ul>
        <h2> Making Process </h2>
        <dl>
         <dt> Water </dt>
         <dd> Warm up 1/4 cup of water </dd>
         <dt> Milk</dt>
         <dd> Add Milk into the water and boil it <dd>
         <dt>Lipton Black Tea</dt>
         <dd>Add Lipton Black Tea into the mix of Boiled water and Milk</dd>
         <dt>Sugar</dt>
         <dd>Add sugar into the mix</dd>
         <dt>Cinnamon and Cardamont</dt>
         <dd>Add Cinnamon and Cardamont and mix it up for 8-9 Minutues</dd>

        </dl>
    </body>
